name: Pepsi 1 Litre
description: Pepsi represents happiness and life. Pepsi is invented in 1898 and was first known as Brad’s Drink, becoming Pepsi-Cola in 1903. The ‘Pepsi' name combines two of its original ingredients, pepsin and kola nuts. Pepsi always has played a very important and favorite role for the youth and indeed, every generation for years and offers itself as a refreshing beverage with a distinctive taste for everyone’s good time. Best Before End: See Shoulder of Bottle. Preparation and Usage: Best served chilled or over ice. Ideal for parties, meals, and celebrations, big and small and every day. Warnings: Pressurized container, please open slowly and handle with care. Recycling info: Bottle. Plastic Widely Recycled
